員多數都係吊住條命先<br />\n去到醫院可能情況已經惡化咁好多<br />\n咁救護車係咪應該要有個醫生喺上面會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncode black? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf6620b25251db02e46d596d9750afcaece305f","tid":443922,"uid":114275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T10:28:49.000Z","msg":"仲要有埋成個藥房 手術室 化驗員 x光 ..."},{"pid":"8ae2a0a9f4344072a235236784b90cdb7388ee71","tid":443922,"uid":53207,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"叫救護車十單有九單根本連醫院都無需要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6925a06f7136acc39e88a9fadba9e5b3da25c41","tid":443922,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T10:43:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>要講急救技巧，醫生未必好過救護員</blockquote><br />\n有急救醫生，specialist其中一門。</blockquote><br />\n我覺得樓主係想講主診醫師</blockquote><br />\n咩主診醫師"},{"pid":"3c390e01292a373154fe7e1da1d7ec77a0502db1","tid":443922,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T11:05:44.000Z","msg":"白車一日接call好多都係鳩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁樣放醫生落去就好無謂<br />\n<br />\n反而我覺得應該真係將「飛行急救醫生」呢個政策普及<br />\n因為而家gfs既flight dr &amp; nurse係星期五六日一先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁其他日子就只得gfs去救人, 始終差咁d<br />\n<br />\n至於人手, 相信外科醫生也有能力擔任flight dr.<br />\n咁變相對急症科醫生需求也可以減少d, 對急症室人手冇咁大壓力<br />\n問題係做得外科既, 肯唔肯花時間去陪你做flight dr姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0625306c24e28da8d0289f66c1f580beffa2648","tid":443922,"uid":36164,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T11:07:15.000Z","msg":"根本就應該將警犬資源放落醫療度<br />\n錢多咗，自然就更多精英學生讀醫<br />\n而家十個狀元九個讀商，<br />\n真係痴線<br />\n<br />\n真係諗唔明點解求其一個散仔行行企企都三萬蚊一個月仲有宿舍住<br />\n不過無計，維穩最重要<br />\n理得你死"}]}